        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Extended Description</title>
            <para>Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0826055">Auxiliary Headlights Circuits From ESC</hotlnk>.
            </para>
            <para>When low auxiliary headlights are requested, the ESC will supply 12 volts to the coils of auxiliary
                high beam micro relay (4002) and auxiliary low beam micro relay (4002).
            </para>
            <para>This will cause both relays to energize switching headlight voltage to the auxiliary headlights.
            </para>
            <para>Ground for the auxiliary headlights is supplied from ground stud (4006) to ground adapter (8800) and
                cavity B of snowplow connector (8102).
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
